quran[58]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,Ndahiriye ku munsi w’izuka
  75,2,Nanarahiriye ku mutima (w’umwemeramana) ugaya nyirawo (kubera guteshuka ku nzira igororotse)
  75,3,Ese umuntu (w’umuhakanyi) akeka ko tutazashobora gukoranya amagufa ye (tumuzura)
  75,4,Nibyo! Dushoboye no kuringaniza imitwe y’intoki ze (imirongo iyiriho igasubira nk’uko yari imeze mbere)
  75,5,Ahubwo umuntu (ahakana izuka) ashaka icyatuma akomeza kwibera mu bwangizi
  75,6,"Arabaza (akerensa) ati \"Uwo munsi w’izuka uzaba ryari"
  75,7,(Uwo munsi uzaba) igihe amaso azakanaguzwa (kubera ubwoba)
  75,8,N’ukwezi kukazima
  75,9,Ndetse izuba n’ukwezi bizahurizwa hamwe (kimwe kinjire mu kindi)
  75,10,"Icyo gihe umuntu azavuga ati \"Ni he ho guhungira"
  75,11,"(Azabwirwa ati) \"Oya! Ntaho guhungira hahari"
  75,12,"Kuri uwo munsi, igarukiro rizaba ari kwa Nyagasani wawe (wenyine)"
  75,13,"Kuri uwo munsi, umuntu azabwirwa ibyo yakoze mbere n’ibyo yaherutse (byaba ibyiza cyangwa ibibi)"
  75,14,Ahubwo umuntu azibera umuhamya w’ibyo yakoze (kuko ingingo z’umubiri we ari zo zizamushinja ibyo yakoze)
  75,15,Kabone n’ubwo yatanga impamvu ze (agamije kwiregura)
  75,16,"(Yewe Muhamadi), ntukanyeganyeze ururimi rwawe ugira ubwira (bwo kuvuga ibyo uhishurirwa, ahubwo ujye utega amatwi wumve ibyo uba uhishurirwa na Malayika Jiburilu)"
  75,17,"Mu by’ukuri, ni twe tuzayikusanyiriza (mu gituza cyawe) kandi ni natwe (tuzakwigisha) kuyisoma (Qur’an)"
  75,18,"Nituyigusomera (binyuze kuri Malayika wacu), ujye ukurikira isomwa ryayo"
  75,19,Hanyuma ni twe (Allah) tuzayigusobanurira
  75,20,(Ibyo mukeka ko mutazazurwa mukanabazwa ibyo mwakoze) si ko biri; ahubwo mukunda ubuzima bwo ku isi butaramba
  75,21,Mukirengagiza imperuka
  75,22,"Kuri uwo munsi, uburanga (bw’abemeramana) buzaba burabagirana"
  75,23,Bureba Nyagasani wabwo
  75,24,"Kuri uwo munsi kandi, uburanga (bw’abahakanyi) buzaba bwijimye"
  75,25,Bibaza ko bagiye guhura n’ishyano
  75,26,Oya! Ahubwo iyo (roho) igeze mu ngoto (igihe cyo gupfa)
  75,27,"Hanyuma hakavugwa ngo \"Ni nde wamutabara (akamurinda urupfu)"
  75,28,Nuko (ugiye gupfa) akamenya ko igihe cyo gutandukana (gupfa) cyageze
  75,29,"Maze (kubera ububabare bwo gukurwamo roho), ukuguru kwe kuzahuzwa n’ukundi"
  75,30,"Kuri uwo munsi, (wowe muntu ukuwemo roho) uzerekezwa kwa Nyagasani wawe"
  75,31,Ariko (umuhakanyi) ntiyigeze yemera ndetse nta n’ubwo yigeze asenga
  75,32,Ahubwo yahinyuye (Qur’an) maze ayitera umugongo
  75,33,Hanyuma akagenda yibona yerekeza mu muryango we
  75,34,Ufite akaga (yewe muntu w’umuhakanyi)! Kandi nanone ufite akaga
  75,35,Nanone ufite akaga (yewe muntu w’umuhakanyi)! Kandi nanone ufite akaga
  75,36,Ese umuntu yibwira ko azarekwa gusa (atabajijwe ibyo yakoze ngo abihemberwe cyangwa ngo abihanirwe)
  75,37,Ese ntiyari intanga zisohorwa
  75,38,"Hanyuma akaba urusoro rw’amaraso, maze Allah akamurema, akanamutunganya (akaba umuntu wuzuye)"
  75,39,"Maze akamuremamo ibitsina bibiri: ikigabo n’ikigore"
  75,40,Ese uwo (Allah ukora ibyo) si we ushoboye kuzura abapfuye
  76,1,Ese nta gihe kirekire cyabayeho umuntu ari ikintu kitazwi
  76,2,"Mu by’ukuri, twaremye umuntu mu ntanga zivanze (iz’umugabo n’iz’umugore) kugira ngo tumugerageze. (Ni yo mpamvu) twamuhaye kumva no kubona"
  76,3,"Mu by’ukuri, twamweretse inzira; abishatse (yahitamo kwemera) agashimira cyangwa agahakana"
  76,4,"Mu by’ukuri, abahakanyi twabateguriye (kuzabahanisha) iminyururu, ingoyi ndetse n’umuriro ugurumana"
  76,5,"Mu by’ukuri, abakiranutsi bazanywera mu kirahuri (cya divayi idasindisha) ivanze (n’amazi y’isoko y’umugezi wo mu ijuru witwa) Kafuur"
  76,6,"(Iyo Kafuur) ni isoko y’amazi abagaragu ba Allah bazanywaho, ikazajya ivubura amazi menshi (bakayerekeza aho bashatse)"
  76,7,"(Abo bakiranutsi) ni abesa imihigo (yabo bahigiye Allah), bakanatinya umunsi ikibi cyazakwira hose (umunsi w’imperuka)"
  76,8,"Bakanaha amafunguro abakene, imfubyi n’imbohe, kabone n’iyo nabo baba bayakeneye"
  76,9,"(Bavuga bati) \"Rwose, turabagaburira kubera gushaka kwishimirwa na Allah. Nta nyiturano cyangwa ishimwe tubashakaho"
  76,10,"Rwose dutinya umunsi ukomeye kandi uzaba urimo ingorane, uturutse kwa Nyagasani wacu, uzatuma (uburanga bw’abahakanyi) bwijima"
  76,11,"Bityo, Allah azabarinda ibibi by’uwo munsi, kandi azabaha umucyo (mu buranga) ndetse n’ibyishimo"
  76,12,Azanabagororera ijuru n’imyambaro y’ihariri kubera ko barangwaga no kwihangana
  76,13,"Bazaba begamye ku bitanda bitatse, (kandi mu Ijuru) ntibazigera bahabona ubushyuhe bw’izuba cyangwa imbeho bikabije"
  76,14,"Kandi igicucu (cy’ibiti byo mu ijuru) kizaba kibegereye, ndetse n’imbuto zabyo zizabegerezwa"
  76,15,Bazazengurutswamo amasahane ya Feza (arimo ibiribwa byiza) n’ibikombe bikozwe mu birahuri
  76,16,"Ibirahuri bikoze muri Feza, byuzuye neza (bijyanye n’ibyifuzo bya buri wese)"
  76,17,Bazanahabwa ikirahuri (cya divayi idasindisha) ivanze na tangawizi
  76,18,Izavomwa mu isoko ryitwa Salisabila